thm (IsElementThereExists ((A x) (B x)) ()
  (↔ (∈ A B) (∃ x (∧ (∈ A x) (= x B))))
# We start with the forward direction. First we prove <code>A ∈ B → ∃ x (x = B ∧ A ∈ B)</code>.
