          (∧ (= x C) (∈ x A))
          (∧ (= x C) (∈ x B))
          ForAllImplicationThereExists
        applySyllogism
# But the two halves of that are equivalent to <code>C ∈ A</code> and <code>C ∈ B</code>, respectively, thanks to <code>MembershipThereExists</code>.
