        applySyllogism
# That gives us <code>∀ x (x ∈ A → ∃ y (x ∈ y ∧ y ∈ C))</code>, which we first turn into <code>∀ x (x ∈ A → x ∈ ⋃ C)</code>,
        x C y Union
        eliminateBiconditionalForward
        (∈ x A) addCommonAntecedent
        x addForAll
        applySyllogism
# and then <code>A ⊆ ⋃ C</code>.
